    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"394485\">suhr</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Stenography.20and.20Lean.204/near/535365668\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I don't care about posture, \\\\\\\\ stagger is just awkward for the left hand.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I have no idea what this means</p>",
