    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/gKTiPDlcaTM5yLMottTUtQyJ/home-row.png\">home-row.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/gKTiPDlcaTM5yLMottTUtQyJ/home-row.png\" title=\"home-row.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"800x580\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/gKTiPDlcaTM5yLMottTUtQyJ/home-row.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>Notice that the columns form the \\\\\\\\ shape.</p>",
        "id": 535366149,
        "sender_full_name": "suhr",
        "timestamp": 1755713213
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>That's nice for the right hand, but not so nice for the left hand. Because for the left hand you would like //// instead.</p>",
        "id": 535366279,
        "sender_full_name": "suhr",
