    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"511228\">Huỳnh Trần Khanh</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Stenography.20and.20Lean.204/near/535366837\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This keyboard is very good <a href=\"https://shop.chenonetta.com/product/jarne-the-ultimate-keyboard/\">https://shop.chenonetta.com/product/jarne-the-ultimate-keyboard/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>it doesn't have a numpad</p>",
